Text: Forgive my dearth of cardiac pathology knowledge. A Papillary Fibroelastoma is unknown territory to me. Excluding the AV channel, I see collagen as an electrical firewall between the atria and the ventricles. Intrusion by a PFE seems likely to open an undesired reentry potential.
